    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Calculates the Root Mean Square of the elements in the input vector. The underlying algorithm is used:</para><para><preformatted>
    Result = sqrt(((pSrc[0] * pSrc[0] + pSrc[1] * pSrc[1] + ... + pSrc[blockSize-1] * pSrc[blockSize-1]) / blockSize));
</preformatted></para><para>There are separate functions for floating point, Q31, and Q15 data types. </para>    </detaileddescription>
